Key Typography Patterns
- Headlines are punchy and direct: "Send money globally for less"
- Supporting text is concise: 2-3 sentences max per description
- Numbers are emphasized with larger/bolder treatment
- Letter-spacing increases slightly on lighter weight text
- Quotes use italic styling with subtle left border accent

