CTA Button Patterns
- Hero CTAs: Large, pill-shaped, high contrast
- Inline CTAs: Default size, often followed by secondary option
- Card CTAs: Text link style with arrow indicator
- Form CTAs: Full-width on mobile, auto-width on desktop

