Calculator Design Principles
1. Real-time updates as user types
2. Fee breakdown shown transparently (not hidden)
3. Exchange rate with time guarantee prominently displayed
4. Arrival estimate provides certainty
5. Comparison to competitors shown below
6. CTA positioned after value is demonstrated


