Transitions
- Default: 0.2s ease for color/shadow changes
- Navigation: 0.35s for slide animations
- Cards: 0.3s for elevation changes
- Loading states: Spinner animations

Focus States
- Visible focus rings for accessibility
- 2px offset, accent color outline
- Tab navigation supported throughout


