Icon Sizing
- Small (16px): Inline with text
- Medium (24px): Buttons, navigation
- Large (32-48px): Feature cards, empty states
- Illustrations (80-120px+): Hero sections, feature highlights

Icon Style
- Consistent stroke width
- Rounded corners to match UI
- Single color (adapts to context)
- Accessible contrast ratios


